          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1723724979961-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>mooli slaw mix</strong> and <strong>rice vinegar</strong> to a bowl with a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled mooli slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1723725022990-x200.jpg",
